  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pre-heat the grill to medium-high</p>\n<p>Add the<strong> mirin</strong>,<strong> Chinese rice wine</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong> and<strong> rice vinegar</strong> to a bowl with the<strong> miso paste</strong> and 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span><strong> sugar</strong> </p>\n<p>Give everything a good mix up until the miso and sugar have dissolved – this is your<strong> miso marinade</strong></p>\n<p>Once dissolved, add the<strong> cod fillets</strong> to the bowl and set aside, turning over occasionally in the marinade</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2134-Step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2134-Step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
